spec.expr:
_stream:{fwb.type=$type,fwb.subtype in (${sub_type:doublequote})}
| fwb.main_type:in(${main_type:doublequote}) AND fwb.action:in(${action:doublequote}) AND fwb.threat_level:in(${threat_level:doublequote})
| ${Logsql:raw}
| user_agent.browser.family:*
| stats by (user_agent.browser.family,fwb.action) count() results 
| sort by (results) desc 
| limit 10
